    },
    "overview": {
        "problem": "Converting images to G-code for robot trajectory planning is a complex process that requires high precision and adaptation to different work environments.",
        "solution": "A system is proposed that uses AI to generate images and convert them to G-code, optimizing trajectory planning.",
        "impact": "This approach enables greater flexibility and efficiency in UR5e robot programming."
    },
